    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head type="title"><app>
                    <lem wit="#KK #B #M">Index XX.</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">Index XI.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">Index XIX.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Index XX., in quo regnum Ludovici primi aperitur</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Index XIX. de successione Ludovici I. filii eius et de conversione Patarenorum</rdg>
                    </app></head>
                <p>
                <s n="1">﻿Ei successit <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #M">Lodovicus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">Ludovicus</rdg>
                    </app> filius, quem ex <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Elisabecta</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Elisabetta</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L2">Elizabetha</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">Elizabeta</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Elisabetha</rdg>
                    </app> uxore <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Poloniae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Polonie</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">(ut iam dictum est)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ut iam dictum est</rdg>
                    </app> regis filia susceperat.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">1 = Th 3.1, cf.
                        Index XIX.4.</note></s>
                <s n="2">Fuit animi magnitudine religioneque atque aliis multis Christiano principe
                    dignis virtutibus parenti non modo simillimus sed etiam par, paternum regnum et
                    gloriam conservavit et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">auxit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">auxisti</rdg>
                    </app>, bello et terribilis et fortunatissimus, pace mitissimus.<note
                        type="critic" corresp="RKK">2 = Th 3.53–54.</note></s>
                <s n="3">Huius frater fuit Andreas ille Siciliae, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">seu</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">sive</rdg>
                    </app> mavis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">dicere</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"/>
                    </app> regni Neapolitani, rex, cui nupsit Ioanna Roberti regis filia, quae
                    Andrea ipso non modo despecto verum etiam abdicato nupsit Philippo principi
                    Tarentinorum, post multas deinde <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ei</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">et</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">illatas</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">illactas</rdg>
                    </app> iniurias ipsum interfecit, ut suo loco ostendi texens <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">catalogum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2">cathalogum</rdg>
                    </app> regum Neapolitanorum.<app>
                        <lem wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"/>
                        <rdg wit="#P"><note type="marginalia"><note type="critic">manu Thomae
                                    Fazello</note>haec ab eo edita nunquam legimus, et cum in
                                superioribus libris non habeantur, his eius verbis fidem non
                                adhibeo</note></rdg>
                    </app></s>
                <s n="4">At vero <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">Lodovicus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ludovicus</rdg>
                    </app> ea de causa cum valido exercitu semel et iterum profectus ad <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ioannae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">Ioanne</rdg>
                    </app> regnum fratris necem ultus est, multisque ibi fortiter glorioseque gestis
                    in suum rediit regnum.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">3–4 = Th 3.9–12, 16, 24,
                        cf. Index XIII.28–29 (de catalogo regum Neapolitanorum).</note></s>
                <s n="5"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Elisabecta</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Elisabetta</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #L2">Elizabetha</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Elisabetha</rdg>
                    </app> quoque eius mater in filii auxilium, antequam illi necis insidiae a dira
                    coniuge pararentur, Neapolim usque navigavit, composita deinde inter filium et
                    nurum concordia Romam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">perrexit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">perexit</rdg>
                    </app>, quo beatorum apostolorum Petri et Pauli corpora veneraretur.<note
                        type="critic" corresp="RKK">5 = Th 3.4.</note></s>
                <s n="6">Duxit hic rex uxorem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #M">Margaritam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Margaritham</rdg>
                    </app> virginem praestanti forma Caroli marchionis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Moraviae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Moravie</rdg>
                    </app> filiam, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ceterum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">coeterum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2">caeterum</rdg>
                    </app> ea immatura morte defuncta duxit <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Elisabectam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Elisabettam</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #L2">Elizabetham</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Elisabetham</rdg>
                    </app> filiam Stephani bani viri genere insignis, ex qua tres ei filiae natae
                    sunt, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">Caterina</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Catharina</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">Catherina</rdg>
                    </app>, Maria, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">Adiuga</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Adviga</rdg>
                    </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">6 = Th 3.52.</note></s>
                <s n="7">Misit copias contra Tartarorum exercitum, qui <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">invaserant</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">invaserunt</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #S2 #S3">Transilvanos</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #M">Transsylvanos</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Transylvanos</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1">Transsilvanos</rdg>
                    </app> et Siculos, illosque <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">(duce Andrea Laczico)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">duce Andrea Laczico</rdg>
                    </app> profligavit; fudit et copias aliquot rebellium, qui in <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Croacia</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Croatia</rdg>
                    </app> et Dalmatia motus magnos exciverant.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">7 =
                        Th 3.6–7.</note></s>
                <s n="8">Duxit in Italiam potentem contra Venetos exercitum, qui sibi occupaverant <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Dalmatiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Dalmatie</rdg>
                    </app> partes maritimas, easque restituere <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">(cum essent ditionis regum Hungariae)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cum essent ditionis regum
                            Hungariae</rdg>
                    </app> recusaverant, aliquot <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">illis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">eis</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">urbes</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">urbe</rdg>
                    </app>, in <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #M">quis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">quibus</rdg>
                    </app> fuit Tarvisium, multaque castella ademit, nec destitit ab armis, donec
                    ei, quae occupata ab illis fuerant, restituerentur.<note type="critic"
                        corresp="RKK">8 = Th 3.8, 26–27.</note></s>
                <s n="9"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Misit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Disit</rdg>
                    </app> et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #M">auxiliares</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">auxillares</rdg>
                    </app> copias summis pontificibus Innocentio, Gregorio et Urbano propterea, quod
                    nonnulli Itali <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">tyranni</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">tyrrani</rdg>
                    </app> multa <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Romanae ecclesiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Romane ecclesie</rdg>
                    </app> oppida suae ditionis fecerant.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">9 = Th
                        3.31.</note></s>
                <s n="10">Expugnavit Bosnenses et Bulgaros, qui ab ipso <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">desciverant</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">defecerant</rdg>
                    </app>, alias multas <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">suscepit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">suscaepit</rdg>
                    </app> expeditiones in suos adversarios, in <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">quibus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #M">quis</rdg>
                    </app> fuit Carolus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">imperator</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">imperarator</rdg>
                    </app>, de quibus omnibus magnam fuit gloriam consecutus.<note type="critic"
                        corresp="RKK">10 = Th 3.33–35.</note></s>
                <s n="11"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">Litfanos</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #M">Litvanos</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Lithvanos</rdg>
                    </app> infestantes Russiam, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app> tum ei parebat, vertit in fugam, deditque <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">deinde</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"/>
                    </app> operam, ut ea gens <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">(cum abhorreret a pietate Christiana)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cum <app>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">abhorreret</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#L2">abhorreat</rdg>
                            </app> a pietate Christiana</rdg>
                    </app> Christi susciperet cultum.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">11 = Th
                        3.29.</note></s>
                <s n="12">Ipsius <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praeterea</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">preterea</rdg>
                    </app> cura effectum est, ut Comani genus hominum ferox <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">et <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P">impium</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B #Z #S2 #S3">imperium</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#L1 #L2 #S1 #M">imperitum</rdg>
                            </app></lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R">(et imperium)</rdg>
                    </app>, qui Tartarorum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S3">ritu</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #M">ritu<add type="insert"> et</add></rdg>
                    </app> absque ulla religione <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">antea</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ante</rdg>
                    </app> vitam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">egerant</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">aegerant</rdg>
                    </app>, ad Christi fidem converterentur.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">12 =
                        Th 3.46.</note></s>
                <s n="13">Navavit et operam, ut Patareni Bosnensis natio abiecta execrabili illa <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #M">Manicheorum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Manichaeorum</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">haeresi</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">heresi</rdg>
                    </app>, cui perdiu <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">inhaeserant</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">inheserant</rdg>
                    </app>, ad fidei veritatem unitatemque redirent, verum perfidi homines haud
                    multo post ab eorum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">haeresiarchis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">heresiarchis</rdg>
                    </app> persuasi ad pristinos redierunt errores.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK"
                        >13 = Th 3.47.</note></s>
                <s n="14">Pepulit ex Hungaria <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Iudaeos</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Iudeos</rdg>
                    </app> eo <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praecipue</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">precipue</rdg>
                    </app>, quod <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK">fenore</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">foenore</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">faenore</rdg>
                    </app> multos ad extremam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">redegerant</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">redaegerant</rdg>
                    </app> inopiam.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">14 = Th 3.41.</note></s>
                <s n="15">Electus et coronatus fuit Poloniae rex, tantum valuit eius apud externos
                        auctoritas.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">15 = Th 3.37.</note></s>
                <s n="16">Sub eo beati Pauli primi <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #R #S1 #M">heremitae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">heremite</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">haeremitae</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L2 #S2 #S3">eremitae</rdg>
                    </app> corpus e <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Venetiis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Venetis</rdg>
                    </app> in Hungariam translatum est, constituit autem complura coenobia, in
                    quibus viverent <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #R #S1 #M">heremitae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">heremite</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">haeremitae</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L2 #S2 #S3">eremitae</rdg>
                    </app>, qui ipsius beati Pauli religionem profiteri se dicunt.<note
                        type="critic" corresp="RKK">16 = Th 3.42–43.</note></s>
                <s n="17"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Obiit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Vbiit</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #L2 #M">mortem anno <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">ab ortu</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #M"/>
                            </app> domini nostri Iesu</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2 #S3"/>
                    </app> Christi <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #L2 #S1 #M">MCCCLXXXII</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R">1382</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S2 #S3">MCCCXXXII</rdg>
                    </app>. <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #L2">tertio</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R">3.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3 #M">III.</rdg>
                    </app> Idus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S3 #M">Septembris</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2">Septembres</rdg>
                    </app>, sepultus est <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Albae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Albe</rdg>
                    </app> in <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">sacello</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R">facello</rdg>
                    </app>, quod vivens <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">extruxerat</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">exstruxerat</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">iuxta</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R"/>
                        <rdg wit="#M">(iuxta)</rdg>
                    </app> aedem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">beatae Mariae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">beate Marie</rdg>
                    </app> virginis, regnavit annos XL.</s>
                <s n="18">Morte eius imminente crinita apparuit stella, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app> tanti principis e vita exitum absque ulla dubitatione significavit.<note
                        type="critic" corresp="RKK">17–18 = Th 3.55.</note></s>
            </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
